genresAdvancedInfo.name: russian plugg
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Russian Plugg is a modern music genre that originated in Russia and is influenced by trap, hip hop, and electronic dance music. The music is characterized by heavy beats, distorted basslines, and aggressive lyrics. Russian Plugg often features autotuned vocals and a fast-paced rhythm, with a focus on energy and intensity. The genre has gained popularity in recent years, particularly among younger audiences.
